{"tid":280360,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"要入熱狗 需過兩關","createTime":"2017-06-12T04:32:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-13T04:54:37.000Z","uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"afb33b1637b2e04659fb117e3af9bd541eb84701","tid":280360,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T04:32:49.000Z","msg":"根據現任主席鄭松泰所言，要成為熱血公民正式成員，你首先要交表，然後還得過兩關。<br />\n<br />\n第一關是派報紙[5]。實體版《熱血時報》每月發行，免費派發，因此需要人手派報。做唔做到「熱狗」，就看你有多積極舉手，比如派足三個月。<br />\n<br />\n「隱藏規則是我們會觀察他（申請人）派幾多次報紙。」鄭松泰說，這是為考核成員熱誠。「因為對普羅大眾來說，派報紙是下欄工作，連續派三個月是很難的事。」<br />\n<br />\n第二關是具備「可能只有熱血公民才明白的價值觀」。鄭松泰解釋：「就是我們的口號，比如『成功之前不要放棄夢想』、『做人最緊要正直』。這些共同話語，是在文化上對組織的認同。」此外，鄭說熱血公民也要擁抱「黃毓民主義」。甚麼是「黃毓民主義」？「其實（我也）不太清楚那是甚麼。」鄭松泰說。翻查傳媒最早使用「黃毓民主義」這個字，是 2012 年《蘋果日報》一篇黃洋達專訪[6]。儘管這篇訪問亦未有明言此一「主義」內涵，唯按前文後理，擁抱「黃毓民主義」應與拜服黃毓民個人魅力有一定關係。<br />\n<br />\n一般黃毓民支持者抗拒被冠「教徒」，但黃洋達並非常人，他二話不說就承認自己是「教徒」，大聲疾呼「擁抱黃毓民主義」！... 對於「教徒」這稱呼，他引以為傲，「其實我好不滿一些對毓民的攻擊，例如話佢搞個人崇拜。搞群眾運動，係需要魅力型領袖吖嘛！」[7]<br />\n<br />\n符合上述兩項要求，你就有資格成為熱血公民大家庭一員。你會得到許多「手足」。不是「同事」、不是「黨友」，而是「手足」。這是熱血公民稱呼成員的方法。「手足」意味眾人不是為熱血公民做事，而是合作做一件更大的事：為香港效力。熱血公民的熱誠不只源於對組織的忠貞，更在於自覺正為香港服務。"},{"pid":"bf8ef8c666e7e5a3c64c21aad6b762eaaaccd6b9","tid":280360,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T04:34:58.000Z","msg":"聽話兩隻字就夠啦"},{"pid":"6497205e7b5cae93c1622f8dbf2507db9c5dff79","tid":280360,"uid":112416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T04:36:31.000Z","msg":"做親熱狗都一定要&ldquo;派報紙&rdquo;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9c51c94c73d89c65d1e68367abc6cb0053e029e","tid":280360,"uid":4880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T04:36:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽話兩隻字就夠啦</blockquote><br />\n咁課金呢?"},{"pid":"8194e0856e865c2940ed94151e348723f9cfc231","tid":280360,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T04:38:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>聽話兩隻字就夠啦</blockquote><br />\n咁課金呢?</blockquote><br />\n聽話自然會交課金"},{"pid":"40b689cf8398f8ed7d3a249c907662570383acd7","tid":280360,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T04:40:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做親熱狗都一定要&ldquo;派報紙&rdquo;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n西走內鬼"},{"pid":"ab62ac8f077ac033a1fa71d287a7e7ba7d92458c","tid":280360,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T04:44:31.000Z","msg":"熱狗派報紙<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔怪得咁鳩<br />\n<br />\n原來幻想下就射"},{"pid":"492a1eb87e4f992e415ff17f7f844cf957743edc","tid":280360,"uid":112416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T04:45:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>熱狗派報紙<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔怪得咁鳩<br />\n<br />\n原來幻想下就射</blockquote><br />\n日日打飛機, 唔虧到派報紙都幾難"},{"pid":"7ecf13550c6c7c5a3e5ad0dfe148b30792ad31ca","tid":280360,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T04:46:23.000Z","msg":"要離開熱狗 只需做人正直"},{"pid":"09120f40414aa8d873b50bc5ab46fe71ed5559ab","tid":280360,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T04:47:49.000Z","msg":"搞群眾運動，係需要魅力型領袖吖嘛<br />\nagger 呢句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雙黃梁天琦後無晒人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8eb39d6432a4b1bbb43dcd616db2056e38e517ad","tid":280360,"uid":2471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T04:48:31.000Z","msg":"『做人最緊要正直』。這些共同話語，是在文化上對組織的認同<br />\n<br />\n講出黎有冇臉紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9d4796696c97c5b33595678bea894e5311de4f5","tid":280360,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T04:56:25.000Z","msg":"不要問只要送"},{"pid":"e7c3071c736b32803c3d26e96fb25f3e40d5b9f4","tid":280360,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T04:56:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不要問只要<span style=\"color: red;\">信</span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"409b496973ea4de7270a41e6483085cb57c9c3ef","tid":280360,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T05:01:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做親熱狗都一定要&ldquo;派報紙&rdquo;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔爭氣笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f95da9b2c2b1fb1f3a31d8ce8676d2206df8191e","tid":280360,"uid":54876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T05:38:53.000Z","msg":"Project mayhem 咪又係咁<br />\n佢講嗰兩樣野唔係問題。<br />\n問題係，呢類組織，只要個大佬一on9，就會全部人陪佢一齊on9"},{"pid":"8f6fd75c6eb1783a39e69870e6f0f9c61cab9b23","tid":280360,"uid":4444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T05:42:13.000Z","msg":"如果係女就要過第三關<br />\n比牙滿食"},{"pid":"8b4d4ccc76028e2d4d3f6294f6843b542a6e92ee","tid":280360,"uid":90863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T05:43:38.000Z","msg":"要有熱誠同忠於領袖<br />\n其實好正常<br />\n<br />\n不過個領袖心術不正咁解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b967a59dcce30db083f608161220e82626b318c","tid":280360,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T05:51:20.000Z","msg":"好幸入你個垃圾邪教呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f36ca2b45282ffede9f4b8d3caabba297b686a1","tid":280360,"uid":26084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T10:42:16.000Z","msg":"屌你老母啦<br />\n選前都掛撚住派報"},{"pid":"14c4a8e9ce3e68106daa10687ee3d1b374120cf8","tid":280360,"uid":8009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T10:45:14.000Z","msg":"要批鬥<br />\n熱衛兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f448f1ae769e94f15f86f6560584584192a809a5","tid":2